<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz Hans Hopplerstat, sein armman, vor
                        ewrem eygenmanne <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan> Hans Hofman, des
                        Rysenheinczen sun, von Galmarsgarten unsicher sey.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan> eygenmanne darczu halten wöllet, daz er den
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sicher auf freuntlich reht, so wil im der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> von <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> slewnigs rehten
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er
                        des ermant wirdt, oder im aber den czum rehten stellen czu
                                <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, czu Winsheim oder czu Pergel, <app><note><q type="inline">ir</q>Ließ: "in".</note></app>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des burggrafen gerihte, wie wol er des niht
                        schuldig wer. Und tut darynne als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des ewr gnedig
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>eria</ex></expan> ii
                                <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> diem <expan>palma<ex>rum.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
